<item>
            <title>[LU-1240] mds-survey README is incorrect</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1240</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The readme for mds-survey (which is the only documentation) is incorrect. &lt;tt&gt;file_count&lt;/tt&gt; is the &apos;number of files per thread&apos;, NOT the total number of files as currently stated:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;file_count     total number of files to test
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://git.whamcloud.com/?p=fs/lustre-release.git;a=blob;f=lustre-iokit/mds-survey/README.mds-survey;h=e66e166ee0028214b979b510844da704d43d7e7d;hb=HEAD#l38&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://git.whamcloud.com/?p=fs/lustre-release.git;a=blob;f=lustre-iokit/mds-survey/README.mds-survey;h=e66e166ee0028214b979b510844da704d43d7e7d;hb=HEAD#l38&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
